   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="MS-B-00005-B-000-00185"/>Herrn <hi rend="latintype">D<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Arthur Schnitzler</hi></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb68" type="place">Wien XVIII</rs></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb168940" type="place">Spöttelga<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>e 7</rs></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="right"><pb facs="MS-B-00005-B-000-00184"/><date>15. 11. 03</date></dateline></opener><p>Danke<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ehr, <salute>lieber Arthur.</salute>  Der <rs ref="#pmb29406" type="org">Berliner Bör<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>en Courier</rs> hat<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chon abgelehnt u. ich habe wenig Hoffnung.
               Die<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>e Bande!</p><p><rs ref="#pmb11740" type="person">Hugo</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chreibt mir, Dein neues <rs type="work" ref="#pmb29985" subtype="implied">Stück</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ei »prachtvoll«. Ich freu mich<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ehr u. wün<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ch Dir
               herzlich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t Glück.</p><p><rs ref="#pmb10986" type="person">Brahm</rs> hat meine <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L01345-1"/><rs type="event" ref="#pmb35263" subtype="implied">Première</rs><note type="commentary" corresp="K_L01345-1">Am <date>12. 12. 1903</date> fand am <rs type="place" ref="#pmb168">Berlin</rs>er
                   <rs type="org" ref="#pmb35597">Deutschen Theater</rs> die <rs type="event" ref="#pmb35263" subtype="implied">Uraufführung</rs> von 
                  von <rs ref="#pmb29983" type="work">Der
                     Meister</rs> statt.</note> auf den <date>12. Dezember</date> ange<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>etzt. Warum plötzlich die<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>e Eile, weiß
               ich nicht. Er kommt Montag im <rs ref="#pmb126" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">Imperial</hi></rs> an.</p><closer>Herzlich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t<lb/>Dein<lb/><signed>H.</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
